---
title: Bacon-Wrapped Pesto and Cheese-Stuffed Chicken with Roasted Potatoes
description: Stuffed chicken is a classic dinner for good reason! Hearty chicken gets a major upgrade when stuffed with a creamy, cheesy filling that is boosted with tangy red pepper pesto, then wrapped in smoky, savoury bacon.
